        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> nvim's terminal on Windows relies on [Pseudoconsole](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/console/pseudoconsoles), which was introduced in version 1809 and was not fully mature at the time.\n\nIs there a win 10 version later than \"1809\" that we should bump `:help supported-platforms` to?",
            "created_at": "2026-04-05T14:02:56Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/32367#issuecomment-4188937929",
